    "description":  "Find out if your business needs to register with HMRC to pay the Economic Crime Levy. ",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Economic Crime Levy applies to businesses that are supervised under the \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/money-laundering-regulations-who-needs-to-register\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eMoney Laundering Regulations\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"who-does-not-need-to-register-with-hmrc\"\u003eWho does not need to register with HMRC\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou do not need to register with HMRC for the Economic Crime Levy if you are supervised under the Money Laundering Regulations by any of the following collection authorities: \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe Financial Conduct Authority (\u003cabbr title=\"Financial Conduct Authority\"\u003eFCA\u003c/abbr\u003e) \u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe Gambling Commission\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eboth HMRC and the \u003cabbr title=\"Financial Conduct Authority\"\u003eFCA\u003c/abbr\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eboth HMRC and the Gambling Commission \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou will need to follow the \u003cabbr title=\"Financial Conduct Authority\"\u003eFCA\u003c/abbr\u003e or Gambling Commission guidance and pay the levy to one of these collection authorities.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDo not register for the Economic Crime Levy, submit yearly Economic Crime Levy returns, or pay the Economic Crime Levy to HMRC.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"who-needs-to-register-with-hmrc\"\u003eWho needs to register with HMRC\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou must register with HMRC if the sum of your UK revenue is more than £10.2 million for all accounting periods ending within a financial year, and your business is regulated either by:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eHMRC for anti-money laundering purposes\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ea professional body for anti-money laundering purposes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe financial year runs from 1 April to 31 March of the following year.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf your accounting period is not 12 months, the £10.2 million threshold is amended pro rata using the number of days in the relevant accounting periods.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou only need to register for the Economic Crime Levy once, but you will need to submit a return and pay the levy each year.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"if-you-are-part-of-a-business-group\"\u003eIf you are part of a business group\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe levy will only apply to members in the group who meet the requirements for registering.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eEach eligible member of the business group must register, submit yearly returns, and pay for the Economic Crime Levy separately.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"if-you-are-part-of-a-partnership\"\u003eIf you are part of a partnership\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe nominated partner must register, submit yearly returns, and pay for the Economic Crime Levy on behalf of the partnership.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-register\"\u003eHow to register\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFind out how to \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/register-for-the-economic-crime-levy\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eregister for the Economic Crime Levy\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
